description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Plezier purrs with a rating of 62, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 186, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 3 for East, 8 for South, and 8 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70623-43884-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [186 Votes, Top 5% Score]
